create table tbl_building_location (selection int,ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT ,country varchar(255),state varchar(255),city varchar(255),street varchar(255), ZIP int,longitude varchar(255),latitude varchar(255),elevation varchar(255),BuildingName varchar(255))

create table tbl_historical_data (ID INTEGER,date_current datetime,hour_current int,minute_current int,distance_from_building varchar(255),temperature varchar(255),humidity varchar(255),bar_pressure varchar(255),wind varchar(255),direction varchar(255),station_name varchar(255))
create table tbl_language_option (ID int, language_id int)

create table tbl_weather_related_values (ID INTEGER ,location varchar(255),distance_from_building varchar(255),last_update_date varchar(255),temp varchar(255),humidity varchar(255),bar_pressure varchar(255),wind varchar(255),direction varchar(255),station_name varchar(255))
